msgid ""
"Duplication is a method to clone an item and pick it up in the same action. It is broadly similar to "
"copy-and-pasting, but it allows you to \"sprinkle\" components over the PCB and it allows you to "
"manually lay out components using the \"Move Exact\" tool (see below) more easily."
