"The \"Move Exact\" tool allows you to move an item (or group of items) by a certain amount, which can be "
"entered in Cartesian or polar formats and which can be entered in any supported units. This is useful "
"when it would otherwise be cumbersome to switch to a different grid, or when a feature is not spaced "
"according to any existing grids."
