#. type: Plain text
#: pcbnew_editing_tools.adoc:38
msgid ""
"To use this tools, select the items you wish to move and then use either the hotkey (defaults to Ctrl-M) "
"or the context menu items to invoke the dialog. You can also invoke the dialog with the hotkey when "
"moving or duplicating items, which can make it easy to repeatedly apply an offset to multiple components."
