#. type: Plain text
#: pcbnew_editing_tools.adoc:73
msgid ""
"The array tool acts on the component under the cursor, or, in GAL mode, on a selection. It can be "
"accessed either via the context menu for the selection or by a keyboard shortcut (defaults to Ctrl-N). "
