#, no-wrap
msgid "Grid arrays"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: pcbnew_editing_tools.adoc:95
msgid ""
"Grid arrays are arrays that lay components out according to a 2-dimensional square grid. This kind of "
"array can also produce a linear array by only laying out a single row or column."
